org.cef.network

类 CefCookieManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cef.network.CefCookieManager

  • public abstract class CefCookieManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Class used for managing cookies. The methods of this class may be called on any thread unless otherwise indicated. (用于管理cookie的类。除非另有说明，否则可以在任何线程上调用此类的方法。)

    • 方法详细资料

      • deleteCookies

        public abstract boolean deleteCookies(java.lang.String url,
                                      java.lang.String cookieName)
        Delete all cookies that match the specified parameters. If both |url| and |cookieName| values are specified all host and domain cookies matching both will be deleted. If only |url| is specified all host cookies (but not domain cookies) irrespective of path will be deleted. If |url| is empty all cookies for all hosts and domains will be deleted. Cookies can alternately be deleted using the visit*Cookies() methods. (删除所有与指定参数匹配的cookie。如果两者| url |和| cookieName |指定的值将删除所有与之匹配的主机和域cookie。如果仅| url |指定所有主机cookie（但不包括域cookie），而与路径无关。如果| url |如果为空，则将删除所有主机和域的所有cookie。可以使用visit * Cookies（）方法来替代删除Cookie。)
        参数:
        url - The cookie URL to delete or null. (-要删除的Cookie URL或为空。)
        cookieName - The cookie name to delete or null. (-要删除的Cookie名称，或者为null。)
        返回:
        False if a non-empty invalid URL is secified or if cookies cannot be accessed. (如果保护了非空的无效URL或无法访问Cookie，则为False。)

      • flushStore

        public abstract boolean flushStore(CefCompletionCallback handler)
        Flush the backing store (if any) to disk. (将后备存储（如果有）刷新到磁盘。)
        参数:
        handler - Callback that will be executed on the UI thread upon completion. (-完成后将在UI线程上执行的回调。)
        返回:
        False if cookies cannot be accessed. (如果无法访问cookie，则为False。)

      • getGlobalManager

        public static final CefCookieManager getGlobalManager()
        Returns the global cookie manager. By default data will be stored at CefSettings.cache_path if specified or in memory otherwise. (返回全局cookie管理器。默认情况下，数据将存储在CefSettings.cache_path中（如果已指定），否则将存储在内存中。)
        返回:
        The global cookie manager. (全局cookie管理器。)

      • setCookie

        public abstract boolean setCookie(java.lang.String url,
                                  CefCookie cookie)
        Sets a cookie given a valid URL and explicit user-provided cookie attributes. This function expects each attribute to be well-formed. It will check for disallowed characters (e.g. the ';' character is disallowed within the cookie value attribute) and fail without setting the cookie if such characters are found. (设置一个具有有效URL和用户明确提供的cookie属性的cookie。此函数期望每个属性的格式正确。它将检查是否存在不允许的字符（例如，在cookie值属性中不允许使用';'字符），并且如果找到了这样的字符，则会在不设置cookie的情况下失败。)
        参数:
        url - The cookie URL. (-Cookie网址。)
        cookie - The cookie attributes. (-Cookie属性。)
        返回:
        False if an invalid URL is specified or if cookies cannot be accessed. (如果指定了无效的URL或无法访问Cookie，则为False。)

      • setSupportedSchemes

        public abstract void setSupportedSchemes(java.util.Vector<java.lang.String> schemes,
                                         boolean includeDefaults)
        Set the schemes supported by this manager. Calling this method with an empty |schemes| value and |includeDefaults| set to false will disable all loading and saving of cookies for this manager. Must be called before any cookies are accessed. (设置此管理器支持的方案。用空的| schemes |调用此方法值和| includeDefaults |设置为false将禁用此管理器的所有cookie加载和保存。在访问任何cookie之前必须先调用它。)
        参数:
        schemes - List of supported schemes. (-支持的方案列表。)
        includeDefaults - If true the default schemes ("http", "https", "ws" and "wss") will also be supported. (-如果为true，则还支持默认方案（“ http”，“ https”，“ ws”和“ wss”）。)

      • visitAllCookies

        public abstract boolean visitAllCookies(CefCookieVisitor visitor)
        Visit all cookies. The returned cookies are ordered by longest path, then by earliest creation date. (访问所有cookie。返回的Cookie按照最长路径排序，然后按照最早的创建日期排序。)
        参数:
        visitor - Callback that will receive cookies on the UI thread. (-回调将在UI线程上接收cookie。)
        返回:
        False if cookies cannot be accessed. (如果无法访问cookie，则为False。)

      • visitUrlCookies

        public abstract boolean visitUrlCookies(java.lang.String url,
                                        boolean includeHttpOnly,
                                        CefCookieVisitor visitor)
        Visit a subset of cookies. The returned cookies are ordered by longest path, then by earliest creation date. (访问部分Cookie。返回的Cookie按照最长路径排序，然后按照最早的创建日期排序。)
        参数:
        url - Results are filtered by the given url scheme, host, domain and path. (-根据给定的网址方案，主机，域和路径过滤结果。)
        includeHttpOnly - If true HTTP-only cookies will also be included in the results. (-如果结果为纯HTTP，则cookie也将包含在结果中。)
        visitor - Callback that will receive cookies on the UI thread. (-回调将在UI线程上接收cookie。)
        返回:
        False if cookies cannot be accessed. (如果无法访问cookie，则为False。)
